Python vs C/C++
===============

Introduction
------------

So far you have learned to use different programming languages and you probably didn't have free choice when writing code. This assignment gives you the opportunity to resume about the key differences of the languages applied in this class: Python and C++ 

1) Where are the differences?
-----------------------------

Try to think of the most important differences of these languages, give some advantages, disadvantages and think of the scopes of application.


2) Emphasize a difference
-------------------------

Think of a short code example where one language provides great advantages over the other. Explain in a few words how this example emphasizes the above mentioned differences.

